          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52858778/" class=" " title="阿晃晃晃晃晃">阿晃晃晃晃晃</a>
                (绝望之为虚妄，正与希望相同。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
